race.comment: READY AND LUCKY (8) failed to back up her narrow sixth in Highway grade when a fading eleventh over 1500m at Rosehill in that class again. Happy to give her another chance now after the sound earlier efforts. SAVOCA (4) scored two-in-a-row before jumping in grade when a plugging sixth over 1250m at Taree in BM84 class. Anna Roper jumps back on and back to his right class for this. SOUTHERLY BUSTER (1) resuming from a spell. Fitter for a recent trial at Scone. Opened last campaign with a third at Newcastle over 1200m. Can feature. TRAPEZE LEGEND (2) should be poised to run a big race first up from a spell following three recent trials - must be respected.
